OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FHeadteacher defends locking
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fschool toilets             
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Wiltshire head teacher has defended  
OL,6, locking toilets during lesson time.    
OL,8,FAnita Ellis said letting pupils go to  
OL,9,Fthe toilet within minutes of a lesson  
OL,10,Fstarting can be "massively disruptive".
OL,12,FRoyal Wootton Bassett Academy is one of
OL,13,Fmany schools across the UK following to
OL,14,Fpractice as they also see a rise in    
OL,15,Fvandalism and vaping during lessons.   
OL,17,FBut a charity has called for the       
OL,18,Fgovernment to look again at how schools
OL,19,Fdecide rules around pupils' access to  
OL,20,Ftoilets.                               
